  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dino has decided that the best place to open his little market is on your desktop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/4922ef97f81df3d001e279d8bb7e85d7.apng?t=1731338000\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/4922ef97f81df3d001e279d8bb7e85d7.poster.avif?t=1731338000\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=96 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customers will ask for specific items and you have to prepare them!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/3193ef1e42d0ff23fa58740dc0d1e431.poster.avif?t=1731338000\" width=616 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/3193ef1e42d0ff23fa58740dc0d1e431.webm?t=1731338000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/3193ef1e42d0ff23fa58740dc0d1e431.mp4?t=1731338000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Once you complete a level, you can choose to rest and chill with your desktop companions</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/d56fa1b5d0996293af369e029046aa1a.poster.avif?t=1731338000\" width=616 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/d56fa1b5d0996293af369e029046aa1a.webm?t=1731338000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/d56fa1b5d0996293af369e029046aa1a.mp4?t=1731338000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use productivity tools like timers and to-do lists to help you focus!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/35be029b553cf230bc8aca42cdcc2bf1.poster.avif?t=1731338000\" width=616 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/35be029b553cf230bc8aca42cdcc2bf1.webm?t=1731338000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/35be029b553cf230bc8aca42cdcc2bf1.mp4?t=1731338000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build carts for new friends!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/dfbbfa466d1f71d1c4b6fe4b6827641b.poster.avif?t=1731338000\" width=616 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/dfbbfa466d1f71d1c4b6fe4b6827641b.webm?t=1731338000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/dfbbfa466d1f71d1c4b6fe4b6827641b.mp4?t=1731338000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose the layout that works best for you!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/8dfee84c47e742f1b0f7903d3787f480.poster.avif?t=1731338000\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/8dfee84c47e742f1b0f7903d3787f480.webm?t=1731338000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/8dfee84c47e742f1b0f7903d3787f480.mp4?t=1731338000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Buy upgrades and automate the process!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/074c814dc85ea07dfb88e68bed68450a.poster.avif?t=1731338000\" width=616 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/074c814dc85ea07dfb88e68bed68450a.webm?t=1731338000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/074c814dc85ea07dfb88e68bed68450a.mp4?t=1731338000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play actively or passively</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use skills to give you a boost!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete challenges and try to be the best market in the world!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock all the achievements!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock all the carts!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch numbers go up!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >For content creators</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twitch, TikTok and Youtube integration to use it as an overlay during your live stream. Create interactive avatars for your chat and play mini-games with them!   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/de9bac544ae6f5e8ac59e90b68b1f5d6.poster.avif?t=1731338000\" width=616 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/de9bac544ae6f5e8ac59e90b68b1f5d6.webm?t=1731338000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/de9bac544ae6f5e8ac59e90b68b1f5d6.mp4?t=1731338000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/6c3cfdf6ead674c9553b67cebca18280.apng?t=1731338000\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098750/extras/6c3cfdf6ead674c9553b67cebca18280.poster.avif?t=1731338000\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=80 /></picture></span></p>",
